00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:31,600
Yes, Father.

572
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,540
With the war reaching this point,

573
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:37,000
we can finally hold our heads high.

574
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,840
When Shanghai is recovered,

575
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:41,200
we will all wear new clothes.

576
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:44,360
I will definitely parade on the streets

577
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:46,800
to shame those traitors.

578
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:49,840
I'm so happy today.

579
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:52,040
Wanfu, do you have wine?

580
00:26:52,040 --> 00:26:52,880
Wine.

581
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:55,920
Yes, we have wine.

582
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:56,720
You want wine, right?

583
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:57,920
Get the wine.

584
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:01,200
The war is won.

585
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,320
Wanfu, Yujiao,

586
00:27:03,760 --> 00:27:05,490
have you ever thought about it?

587
00:27:06,280 --> 00:27:07,840
After the war is won,

588
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,760
what are your plans?

589
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:10,930
Take it easy.

590
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:11,880
Sit down.

591
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,720
I have something to tell you.

592
00:27:17,320 --> 00:27:20,560
In the future, when the war is won,

593
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:23,800
do you have any long-term plans?

594
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:29,000
Wanfu.

595
00:27:30,280 --> 00:27:31,810
Have you ever thought about

596
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:35,720
staying with Yujiao in the future?

597
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,080
Why are you staring at me?

598
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,160
I'm not confused.

599
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,440
It's not just because of

600
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,480
today's battle report.

601
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:51,600
I've thought about this for a long time.

602
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,680
Wanfu.

603
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,250
Actually, that day,

604
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:01,440
when Yueming called you Dad,

605
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:05,760
my own grandson called you Dad.

606
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:10,360
But I wasn't angry or disgusted.

607
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:13,520
I was full of joy.

608
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:17,440
Yujiao, I'm old.

609
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:20,280
How my health really is,

610
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:22,560
you don't have to hide it from me.

611
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,800
I know it very well myself.

612
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:28,120
I think if I'm gone,

613
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:31,320
how will you and Yueming live?

614
00:28:31,760 --> 00:28:32,440
Father.

615
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,520
This kid Wanfu,

616
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,560
even though I scold him,

617
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:37,920
I know him.

618
00:28:38,360 --> 00:28:39,160
In prison,

619
00:28:39,280 --> 00:28:41,200
we were together every day.

620
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:43,960
I taught him the 'Thousand Character Classic',

621
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:45,420
and told him about Qu Yuan.

622
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,840
I gave him

623
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:50,480
the early education that even Yunkui didn't get.

624
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:53,120
This made up for my regrets.

625
00:28:54,120 --> 00:28:55,640
From that day on,

626
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:58,920
I treated him like my own son.

627
00:29:00,560 --> 00:29:02,160
Along our journey together,

628
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,840
time is the best measure

629
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,840
to test a person.

630
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:11,120
Wanfu is a reliable boy.

631
00:29:11,560 --> 00:29:12,760
He is a good boy.

632
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:15,120
You are a good girl too.

633
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:17,000
In the past,

634
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,480
people would tell you to remain a widow.

635
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:21,410
To hell with remaining a widow.

636
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:24,160
As long as you live well,

637
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:27,120
and let Yueming grow up

638
00:29:27,680 --> 00:29:29,840
safely and healthily,

639
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:37,400
I, Zhang Ruxian, will have no regrets in this life.

640
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:43,680
No regrets at all.

641
00:29:53,040 --> 00:29:54,080
Master,

642
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:56,200
I know exactly

643
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,440
who I am.

644
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:02,960
I'm just a little bug.

645
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:06,600
There are many things and words

646
00:30:07,600 --> 00:30:09,660
that I don't even dare to think about,

647
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,080
let alone say.

648
00:30:11,360 --> 00:30:12,880
These years,

649
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:15,200
when we were outside,

650
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:17,160
I called you Father.

651
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,000
But back home,

652
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,760
I always called you Master.

653
00:30:22,360 --> 00:30:24,520
I was afraid of crossing the line.

654
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:28,200
But today you said

655
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,600
you treated me as your son.

656
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,480
Actually,

657
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:38,490
I've considered you my father for a long time.

658
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,360
My real father.

659
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:44,080
The brigade commander is gone.

660
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:46,520
In recent years,

661
00:30:47,320 --> 00:30:50,760
Xiaoyue hasn't sent any news.

662
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:53,280
It's highly likely that she's...

663
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,240
Yueming,

664
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:03,400
the first person he saw when he was born,

665
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:05,050
besides his mother,

666
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:07,440
was me.

667
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:11,440
My greatest wish in life, Meng Wanfu,

668
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:14,440
is to raise Yueming

669
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:16,880
and let him grow up

670
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,570
healthy and strong.

671
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:34,960
Yujiao,

672
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,560
what do you think?

673
00:31:40,040 --> 00:31:41,120
Father,

674
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:44,200
you know what I used to be like.

675
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:48,000
The hardships I've suffered these years

676
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,480
are more than what I had in my first 20 years.

677
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:54,250
These years, all I think about every day is

678
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:58,040
how to keep our family alive,

679
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:00,280
how to let you

680
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,120
live a good life,

681
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:04,240
and how to let Yueming

682
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:06,960
live well.

683
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,170
As for other things,

684
00:32:15,360 --> 00:32:16,440
Wanfu is very good.

685
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:19,240
Exceptionally good.

686
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:22,080
To be honest,

687
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:24,960
when I first saw you,

688
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,490
I really looked down on you.

689
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:29,480
But everything you've done for the Zhang Family,

690
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:31,520
I've seen it all.

691
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:34,080
I said thank you to you before,

692
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,210
but you said no need.

693
00:32:35,360 --> 00:32:36,120
Now,

694
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,760
I still want to say thank you.

695
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:43,000
Without you, there wouldn't be me,

696
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,980
and we wouldn't be where we are today.

697
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,480
On that rainy night,

698
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:52,360
you carried me on your back to Lutai Restaurant

699
00:32:52,360 --> 00:32:54,160
and made me a bowl of hot noodles.

700
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,720
I said,

701
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,170
it's not enough.

702
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,900
Ever since that night, I've known

703
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,650
you are the one I can rely on.

704
00:33:02,480 --> 00:33:03,200
But,

705
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:07,040
I still have to tell the truth.

706
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:08,800
Even now,

707
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,800
Yunkui still holds

708
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:14,260
