709
00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:18,920
Father, I thank you very much.

710
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:21,720
Thank you for being so open-minded.

711
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:24,530
I know you treat me like your own daughter.

712
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:27,480
Thank you for opening this door for me.

713
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:29,400
But if it's because

714
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:33,280
Wanfu treats me well that I choose him,

715
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:38,160
it would be irresponsible to him.

716
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:41,530
It would also be irresponsible to Yunkui.

717
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:42,400
Likewise,

718
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:45,780
it would be irresponsible to myself.

719
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:49,440
I understand.

720
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:51,960
You are all good kids.

721
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:55,920
Good, honest kids.

722
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,880
I will wait for you.

723
00:33:58,840 --> 00:33:59,880
Come,

724
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:02,120
let's have a drink.

725
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:03,720
Come, let's drink.

726
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,700
Father, we agreed,

727
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:08,199
just one drink tonight.

728
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:09,840
Just one.

729
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:11,840
Kids,

730
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:13,239
this drink is

731
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:16,639
for the liberation of Shanghai.

732
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,080
Cheers!

733
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:33,000
Smile a bit, don't pull a long face.

734
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,880
Shout!

735
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:34,960
Shout! Shout!

736
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,360
You guys shout!

737
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:46,120
Let's go, quick!

738
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,120
Go! Go!

739
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:49,360
Go!

740
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:50,199
Hurry up.

741
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:53,880
Hurry up.

742
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,040
Hurry up.

743
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:07,320
Master can get out of bed now,

744
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:10,240
