745
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:12,040
What if he finds out we're lying to him one day?

746
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:13,040
What should we do?

747
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:15,410
I've been thinking about this too.

748
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:17,240
I want to send Father

749
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,440
over to Ms. Zeng's place.

750
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:23,080
Go quickly!

751
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:43,640
Wanfu!

752
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,560
Yujiao!

753
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:51,920
Long live the Empire of Japan!

754
00:36:16,200 --> 00:36:17,320
Yueming,

755
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:21,000
Grandpa will take you to fly a kite.

756
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:30,240
Yueming!

757
00:36:38,720 --> 00:36:40,600
Yueming!

758
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:56,520
Long live! Long live! Long live!

759
00:37:26,040 --> 00:37:31,080
Long live! Long live the Empire of Japan! Long live! Long live!

760
00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:42,760
Long live! Long live! Long live!

761
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:46,040
Long live the Chinese army!

762
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:49,760
Japanese devils, get out of China!

763
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:52,520
China will win!

764
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:56,600
Liberation of Shanghai!

765
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:58,920
China will win!

766
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:01,720
China will...

767
00:38:44,720 --> 00:38:47,480
That's not it.

768
00:38:56,040 --> 00:38:59,200
That's not it.

769
00:38:59,640 --> 00:39:00,760
Look, there's someone on the roof.

770
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:01,880
Grandpa,

771
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:04,560
fly a kite there.

772
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:06,240
China will win!

773
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:06,960
Father!

774
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,010
Master! Father!

775
00:39:08,440 --> 00:39:11,360
China will win.

776
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:13,560
Shanghai is liberated.

777
00:39:14,040 --> 00:39:15,040
Father.

778
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,440
Father, what are you doing up there?

779
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:16,920
Master.

780
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:18,240
Master, what are you doing?

781
00:39:18,240 --> 00:39:19,680
Master, what are you doing?

782
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:22,000
Father, Master.

783
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,200
Master.

784
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:24,560
Get lost, you bastard.

785
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:25,520
Master, Father.

786
00:39:25,520 --> 00:39:27,520
Master, what are you doing, Master?

787
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:29,680
Shanghai is liberated.

788
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:33,200
Long live China.

789
00:39:34,200 --> 00:39:36,680
China will win.

790
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:38,760
Master, Father.

791
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:19,760
China will win.

792
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:25,440
Master, Father.

793
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:56,520
Father.

794
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:07,800
Mother.

795
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:13,440
Master, Father.

796
00:42:55,240 --> 00:42:56,570
Father has passed away.

797
00:42:57,080 --> 00:42:58,740
You can sleep in Father's bed.

798
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:01,720
In my heart,

799
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,000
